description: Local folks are just drooling over the absolutely delicious assortment of smoked meats and comfort foods that are being cooked up at the DrewbaQ truck. After searching all around for BBQ of sufficient quality without any luck, Drew decided to take matters into his own hands. Receiving the sincere and earnest praise of friends and family who adored his take on classic creations, he finally gained the confidence to take his ‘Q out to the streets. And with the care and quality that Drew puts into his food, it’s no surprise that he and his truck are the newest sensation. You simply gotta trek on out to DrewbaQ to indulge in Pulled Pork Egg Rolls, Brisket & Mac ‘n Cheese Sandwiches, Smoked Turkey, Cornbread, and so much more.
name: DrewbaQ Food Truck
